    Sessions <--> Registry
    LogAgg --> Registry

    Engine -->|Dispatch tasks / poll| W1
    Engine -->|Dispatch tasks / poll| W2
    Engine -->|Dispatch tasks / poll| WN
    W1 -->|Heartbeat / Register| Registry
